<div class="fade-text-container">
  <div class="fade-text" id="fadeText1">CX kann innerhalb von 30 Tagen ab Lieferdatum mit dem R端cksendeetikett, das wir an CX senden, zur端ckgeben</div>
  <div class="fade-text" id="fadeText2">Schlafen Sie ruhig, wir halten Ihnen den R端cken frei - Kostenloser Versand f端r alle unsere Produkte</div>
  {% for block in section.blocks %}
    <div class="fade-text">{{ block.settings.text }}</div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<style>
.fade-text-container {
  position: relative;
  height: 60px; /* Adjust height to fit text */
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: #72477c; /* Background color */
  color: white; /* Text color */
}

.fade-text {
  position: absolute;
  width: 100%;
  opacity: 0;
  animation: fadeInOut 15s infinite; /* Adjusted duration for smoother transitions */
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 65px; /* Adjust to vertically center text */
}

@keyframes fadeInOut {
  0%, 33%, 100% { opacity: 0; }
  5%, 28% { opacity: 1; }
}

.fade-text:nth-child(2) {
  animation-delay: 8s; /* Adjust delay for timing */
}

.fade-text:nth-child(3) {
  animation-delay: 2s; /* Add delay for additional text block */
}
</style>

